, shown on an RTX 4090 PC, suggests the game may feature character customization, with English voice acting confirmed, while other languages are still in development. Further details remain undisclosed. Varsapura focuses on immersive storytelling and [&#8230;]]]></description>
      <content:encoded><![CDATA[<figure><img width="1024" height="654" src="https://i0.wp.com/technode.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/2020121632700294-scaled.jpg?fit=1024%2C654&amp;ssl=1" class="attachment-rss-image-size size-rss-image-size wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" srcset="https://i0.wp.com/technode.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/2020121632700294-scaled.jpg?w=2560&amp;ssl=1 2560w, https://i0.wp.com/technode.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/2020121632700294-scaled.jpg?resize=300%2C192&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/technode.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/2020121632700294-scaled.jpg?resize=768%2C491&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/technode.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/2020121632700294-scaled.jpg?resize=1536%2C981&amp;ssl=1 1536w, https://i0.wp.com/technode.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/2020121632700294-scaled.jpg?resize=2048%2C1309&amp;ssl=1 2048w, https://i0.wp.com/technode.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/2020121632700294-scaled.jpg?resize=1200%2C767&amp;ssl=1 1200w, https://i0.wp.com/technode.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/2020121632700294-scaled.jpg?resize=1024%2C654&amp;ssl=1 1024w, https://i0.wp.com/technode.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/2020121632700294-scaled.jpg?resize=1568%2C1002&amp;ssl=1 1568w, https://i0.wp.com/technode.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/2020121632700294-scaled.jpg?resize=400%2C256&amp;ssl=1 400w, https://i0.wp.com/technode.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/2020121632700294-scaled.jpg?resize=706%2C451&amp;ssl=1 706w, https://i0.wp.com/technode.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/2020121632700294-scaled.jpg?w=2340&amp;ssl=1 2340w, https://i0.wp.com/technode.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/2020121632700294-scaled.jpg?fit=1024%2C654&amp;ssl=1&amp;w=370 370w" sizes="(max-width: 34.9rem) calc(100vw - 2rem), (max-width: 53rem) calc(8 * (100vw / 12)), (min-width: 53rem) calc(6 * (100vw / 12)), 100vw" /></figure>
<p>miHoYo today unveiled a 31-minute gameplay demo for its upcoming open-world title Varsapura, developed using Unreal Engine 5. The demo, shown on an RTX 4090 PC, suggests the game may feature character customization, with English voice acting confirmed, while other languages are still in development. Further details remain undisclosed. Varsapura focuses on immersive storytelling and realistic visuals, with the protagonist&#8217;s appearance adapting based on player preferences. Combat features a three-character switching system, and the game showcases unique weapon designs. The word Varsapura is derived from Sanskrit, with &#8220;varsa&#8221; meaning &#8220;rain&#8221; and &#8220;pura&#8221; translating to &#8220;city,&#8221; so the overall meaning can be understood as &#8220;City of Rain.&#8221; [<a href="https://weibo.com/7721481977/QePsrA1y0?refer_flag=1001030103_">Varsapura</a>, in Chinese]</p>
]]></content:encoded>
